data.description: Embrace the exceptional Lake View vacation home in the serene Indian Point vicinity, a short distance from Silver Dollar City. The moment you step inside, you'll be struck by the extensive remodel, rendering this property a perfect spot for year-round enjoyment, whether it's full-time living or a vacation getaway. Kids will be delighted with their private onsite playground. What sets this home apart is its remarkable design, capable of accommodating two families or serving as an exceptional entertainment hub for your family and guests, thanks to separate kitchens and bedrooms on each floor. Both levels offer expansive decks that stretch the entire front of the house, with the upper floor offering a captivating lake view year-round. This property is conveniently within walking distance to Table Rock Lake, making it a paradise for lake aficionados. As a bonus, an additional adjacent lot is included with this property, and some furniture is part of the package. Please note that vacation rentals are not permitted. If you're a fan of lake living, this home is tailor-made for you.
